highlights.text: “Ghungroo (From "War")” by Vishal-Shekhar, Arijit Singh, Shilpa Rao, and Kumaar is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kolkata, up 31 spots at #63.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Kolkata. “Kesariya” is the highest at #3.
“Ghodey Pe Sawaar (From "Qala")” by Amit Trivedi, Amitabh Bhattacharya, and Sireesha Bhagavatula is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kolkata at #31.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Kolkata the longest, at 64 weeks straight.
